1
00:00:00,001 --> 00:00:02,001
Waktunya kerja.

2
00:00:03,011 --> 00:00:09,441
{On that day, a dying sun rose above the multitude of nations.}Hari itu, kulihat mentari sayu
bersinar di atas berbagai negara.

3
00:00:22,471 --> 00:00:23,711
Apa ini?

4
00:00:29,171 --> 00:00:31,251
{As written in the Book of Revelations,}Seperti yang ditulis di Buku Pencerahan,

5
00:00:31,251 --> 00:00:33,721
{"When the sun has died five times,}"Ketika matahari telah mati sebanyak 5 kali,

6
00:00:33,721 --> 00:00:36,571
{a red lake will emerge to the west of a city}danau merah akan muncul di sebelah barat kota

7
00:00:36,571 --> 00:00:39,181
{with a name both new and old."}dengan nama baru dan lama."

8
00:00:40,581 --> 00:00:45,321
{"It will be the sign that the fifth angel has descended upon this world.}"Itu akan jadi pertanda bahwa malaikat kelima diturunkan ke dunia ini.

9
00:00:52,421 --> 00:00:54,701
{The angel is the Hawk of Darkness.}Malaikat tersebut adalah Rajawali Kegelapan.

10
00:00:55,991 --> 00:00:59,531
{He is the master of the sinful black sheep.}Dia adalah tuan bagi
domba-domba hitam penuh dosa.

11
00:01:00,261 --> 00:01:03,231
{And the king of the blind white sheep.}Dan raja dari para domba putih yang buta.

12
00:01:03,911 --> 00:01:09,081
Dia akan mengantarkan era kegelapan untuk menyelubungi dunia."

13
00:01:22,221 --> 00:01:25,721
Pendekar Pedang Bertanda

14
00:03:10,251 --> 00:03:11,671
Hei, nak!

15
00:03:11,671 --> 00:03:13,391
Bawakan lagi birnya! Cepat!

16
00:03:16,161 --> 00:03:17,381
Sial...

17
00:03:17,381 --> 00:03:19,151
Kenapa aku?

18
00:03:19,971 --> 00:03:22,081
Makanan kami mana?

19
00:03:22,081 --> 00:03:23,241
Diam kau!

20
00:03:23,241 --> 00:03:24,561
Lagi sibuk ini, tahu nggak!

21
00:03:24,891 --> 00:03:26,121
H-Hei, awas!

22
00:03:26,991 --> 00:03:29,031
Jangan kejang-kejangan melulu!

23
00:03:29,031 --> 00:03:30,501
Nanti nggak kena!

24
00:03:32,441 --> 00:03:35,441
Ayo, lempar pisaunya lagi! Cepat!

25
00:03:35,441 --> 00:03:37,761
Oke, kuterima tantanganmu, njing.

26
00:03:37,761 --> 00:03:38,891
Lepaskan aku!

27
00:03:38,891 --> 00:03:41,201
Aku akan mengigitmu
tembus sampai ke arteri!

28
00:03:41,201 --> 00:03:44,111
Aku akan menghancurkan
mulutmu yang sombong itu.

29
00:03:44,111 --> 00:03:47,291
{No, thanks! No, no, no!}Tidak, terima kasih! Tidak, tidak, tidak!

30
00:03:45,691 --> 00:03:47,691
Hei.

31
00:03:46,471 --> 00:03:47,541
Huh?

32
00:03:47,541 --> 00:03:50,151
{Are you trying to make me clean up corpses?}Kau mencoba membuatku membersihkan mayat-mayat?

33
00:03:50,151 --> 00:03:52,151
Bagaimana kalau iya?

34
00:03:51,311 --> 00:03:54,321
{I came with you guys because
I heard you were mercs.}Aku mengikuti kalian karena kudengar kalian ini tentara bayaran.

35
00:03:54,321 --> 00:03:57,041
Tapi tingkahmu cuma seperti bandit dan preman pasar!

36
00:03:57,321 --> 00:03:59,551
{I want to make a name with my sword!}Aku ingin membuat nama dengan pedangku!

37
00:03:59,551 --> 00:04:00,601
Oh?

38
00:04:01,201 --> 00:04:04,801
{Anyway, I can't do this anymore!}Pokoknya, aku tidak mau lagi bekerja seperti ini!

39
00:04:11,061 --> 00:04:13,691
{Don't be so full of yourself, you sniveling brat!}Jangan sombong dulu, bocah tengik!

40
00:04:14,021 --> 00:04:16,221
Setelah yang semua kau katakan,

41
00:04:16,221 --> 00:04:18,821
{you think you'll get out of this in one piece?}kau pikir bisa kabur dengan selamat?

42
00:04:18,821 --> 00:04:20,941
Bajingan, bangsat—

43
00:04:21,311 --> 00:04:23,391
Kau akan menjadi target kami selanjutnya.

44
00:04:24,731 --> 00:04:26,731
Hei.

45
00:04:25,531 --> 00:04:27,531
Ya?

46
00:04:26,291 --> 00:04:27,491
Kau menghalangi jalanku.

47
00:04:27,491 --> 00:04:28,821
Bisa minggir nggak?

48
00:04:28,821 --> 00:04:30,821
Huh?

49
00:04:29,761 --> 00:04:31,411
Kau pikir bicara pada siapa—

50
00:04:33,661 --> 00:04:35,661
Bajingan!

51
00:04:34,571 --> 00:04:35,811
Jangan seenaknya sendiri!

52
00:04:43,161 --> 00:04:44,181
Apa?

53
00:05:02,821 --> 00:05:04,571
Maaf atas keributannya.

54
00:05:04,571 --> 00:05:06,631
Dan juga, bisa tolong penuhi
kantong ini dengan air?

55
00:05:06,631 --> 00:05:08,631
{And a bottle of rum.}Dan sebotol miras.

56
00:05:07,851 --> 00:05:09,481
Y-Ya.

57
00:05:42,841 --> 00:05:44,171
Hmm...

58
00:05:47,751 --> 00:05:49,751
Oh!

59
00:05:51,861 --> 00:05:53,631
Akhirnya ketemu!

60
00:05:56,501 --> 00:05:58,581
Setelah menolong seseorang,
jangan tinggalkan mereka!

61
00:05:58,581 --> 00:06:00,651
Harusnya kau bertanggung
jawab sampai akhir!

62
00:06:04,341 --> 00:06:05,761
Oh, hei...

63
00:06:06,171 --> 00:06:08,631
Barang yang kelihatan berat ini apa?

64
00:06:11,641 --> 00:06:14,581
Uh...

65
00:06:14,581 --> 00:06:17,061
Namaku Puck! Salam kenal!

66
00:06:17,061 --> 00:06:19,341
Aku bersama rombongan seniman keliling,

67
00:06:19,341 --> 00:06:21,641
tapi mereka diserang oleh para bandit itu.

68
00:06:21,641 --> 00:06:25,541
{I've been stuffed in a birdcage and dipped in a jug of ale.}Aku dimasukkan ke kandang burung dan ditempatkan ke tong miras.

69
00:06:25,541 --> 00:06:28,151
Aneh juga aku masih hidup!

70
00:06:28,151 --> 00:06:30,571
Um... Um...

71
00:06:30,571 --> 00:06:34,111
Menurutku, para bandit itu memiliki kawanan di dekat sini.

72
00:06:34,111 --> 00:06:36,181
Di tempat lain, mereka memiliki orang-orang yang terampil.

73
00:06:36,181 --> 00:06:38,931
Kalau tidak segera pergi, bisa jadi kau berada dalam masalah!

74
00:06:40,671 --> 00:06:41,951
Aduh!

75
00:06:41,951 --> 00:06:43,721
Apa kau yang kau lakukan, bego?!

76
00:06:43,721 --> 00:06:45,421
Jangan bicara padaku...

77
00:06:46,761 --> 00:06:48,761
Kuhancurkan kau nanti.

78
00:06:50,211 --> 00:06:52,211
Hmph!

79
00:07:02,461 --> 00:07:03,561
Orang itu...

80
00:07:12,791 --> 00:07:14,791
Sial...

81
00:07:13,741 --> 00:07:15,411
Kayaknya nyasar, nih.

82
00:07:35,481 --> 00:07:36,881
{Would you like to hop on?}Apa kau ingin naik?

83
00:07:36,881 --> 00:07:39,181
{It can't be easy,
dealing with this rain at night.}Terjebak hujan di malam hari pasti menyusahkan.

84
00:07:39,181 --> 00:07:40,901
Tidak apa-apa. Tinggalkan aku sendiri.

85
00:07:40,901 --> 00:07:42,651
Tidak perlu menolak.

86
00:07:42,651 --> 00:07:44,691
{My daughter wishes to help you, too.} Anakku juga ingin membantumu.

87
00:07:45,081 --> 00:07:48,191
{I'm refusing for your own good.} Aku menolak untuk kebaikanmu.

88
00:07:50,091 --> 00:07:53,701
{You see, I'm possessed... By evil spirits.} Aku ini kerasukan... oleh roh jahat.

89
00:07:54,691 --> 00:07:56,521
{That's unfortunate.} Sayang sekali.

90
00:07:56,521 --> 00:07:58,561
{But there's no need for concern.} Tapi jangan khawatir.

91
00:07:58,561 --> 00:08:00,951
Tuhan sudah menjagaku.

92
00:08:00,951 --> 00:08:03,071
{And a spirit of good fortune.} Dan juga ada roh keberuntungan.

93
00:08:04,671 --> 00:08:06,961
{Now, hop on...} Nah, naiklah...

94
00:08:22,551 --> 00:08:24,481
{A man with a black prosthetic arm?} Seorang pria dengan lengan palsu hitam?

95
00:08:24,481 --> 00:08:25,811
{I'm not lying!} Aku tidak bohong!

96
00:08:25,811 --> 00:08:28,111
{I swear he had a monster's strength!} Dia memiliki kekuatan monster!

97
00:08:28,111 --> 00:08:29,941
{Quit your yappin'.} Hentikan ocehanmu.

98
00:08:29,941 --> 00:08:31,191
{We get it.} Kami mengerti.

99
00:08:31,191 --> 00:08:34,441
{We called in thirty or so skilled
men to wait for him.} Kami memanggil 30 lebih orang
terampil untuk menunggunya.

100
00:08:34,441 --> 00:08:36,401
{We'll finish him soon enough.} Kami akan segera menghabisinya.

101
00:08:36,401 --> 00:08:40,241
{In any event, couldn't we have
found a better meeting spot?} Selain itu, apa kita tidak bisa mencari tempat berkumpul yang lebih baik?

102
00:08:40,241 --> 00:08:42,241
Huh?

103
00:08:40,631 --> 00:08:42,001
Kalian tahu ini?

104
00:08:42,001 --> 00:08:44,001
{Know what?} Tahu apa?

105
00:08:42,961 --> 00:08:48,201
{These parts used to be home to evil cultists
that worshiped forest spirits.} Bagian ini dulu digunakan sebagai rumah bagi pemuja kejahatan yang menyembah roh hutan.

106
00:08:48,201 --> 00:08:49,351
{Evil cultists?} Pemuja kejahatan?

107
00:08:49,351 --> 00:08:53,841
{It's said they held sacrificial rituals
where they staked your intestines} Dikatakan mereka mengadakan upacara
persembahan dengan menggunakan isi perutmu

108
00:08:53,841 --> 00:08:58,021
{to a tree, and then made
you run around the trunk.} pada sebuah pohon, kemudian memintamu untuk mengelilingi batangnya.

109
00:08:58,511 --> 00:09:01,271
{This is one of those trees.} Ini adalah salah satu pohonnya.

110
00:09:01,271 --> 00:09:03,251
Sebaiknya hentikan leluconmu.

111
00:09:03,251 --> 00:09:06,221
{The place feels haunted enough as it is...} Tempatnya terasa cukup angker...

112
00:09:06,221 --> 00:09:09,371
{There are rumors that monsters
appear in these forests, too.} Ada isu yang mengatakan monster
juga akan muncul di hutan ini.

113
00:09:09,371 --> 00:09:10,541
{Monsters?} Monster?

114
00:09:10,541 --> 00:09:14,271
{In this day and age, there are wars,
disasters, and piles of corpses,} Di zaman ini, ada peperangan,
bencana, dan banyak mayat,

115
00:09:14,271 --> 00:09:16,851
{no matter where you go.} kemana pun kau pergi.

116
00:09:16,851 --> 00:09:20,031
{It wouldn't be surprising if evil
spirits and the like appear.} Tidak heran kalau roh jahat
dan semacamnya muncul.

117
00:09:28,211 --> 00:09:29,331
{What?} Apa?

118
00:09:29,331 --> 00:09:31,961
{I got here first.} Aku duluan yang tiba di sini.

119
00:09:31,961 --> 00:09:34,131
{I don't want to hear any complaints!} Aku tidak ingin mendengar keluhan apapun!

120
00:09:36,191 --> 00:09:38,091
Kalau berkenan, silakan sambil dinikmati.

121
00:09:38,091 --> 00:09:39,971
{It's wine we made ourselves.} Anggur yang kami buat sendiri.

122
00:09:39,971 --> 00:09:41,231
{It will warm you up.} Khasiatnya akan menghangatkanmu.

123
00:09:41,791 --> 00:09:43,041
Aku tidak butuh.

124
00:09:43,041 --> 00:09:45,041
{But...} Tapi...

125
00:09:44,391 --> 00:09:47,471
{There are many dangers at night.} Ada banyak bahaya saat malam hari.

126
00:09:49,941 --> 00:09:52,711
{Jeez, don't waste people's goodwill...} Jangan sia-siakan kebaikan orang lain, dong.

127
00:09:52,711 --> 00:09:53,861
{Fine, give it to me—} Kalau begitu, serahkan itu padaku—

128
00:09:54,911 --> 00:09:57,431
{Um, is that scar from battle?} Emm, apa itu bekas luka pertempuran?

129
00:09:57,431 --> 00:09:59,971
{I was bitten by an evil spirit.} Aku tergigit oleh roh jahat.

130
00:09:59,971 --> 00:10:01,641
Tapi... apa benar?

131
00:10:01,641 --> 00:10:06,461
{Come, now... Please don't scare
my daughter too much.} Hei... Jangan menakut-nakuti anakku.

132
00:10:06,461 --> 00:10:07,961
{What is your name?} Siapa namamu?

133
00:10:07,961 --> 00:10:09,211
Guts.

134
00:10:09,211 --> 00:10:10,651
{I am Adolf.} Aku Adolf.

135
00:10:10,651 --> 00:10:12,311
{My daughter is Collette.} Anakku Collette.

136
00:10:12,311 --> 00:10:16,971
{By the way, is that thing on your back a...} Ngomong-ngomong, apa benda di punggungmu itu...

137
00:10:21,171 --> 00:10:22,471
Lupakan saja.

138
00:10:22,471 --> 00:10:25,841
{By the way, I was watching
you at the tavern earlier.} Ngomong-ngomong, tadi aku melihatmu di bar.

139
00:10:25,841 --> 00:10:27,511
{I don't approve of violence,} Aku tidak suka kekerasan,

140
00:10:27,511 --> 00:10:30,231
{but saving the elven child was a noble act.} tapi menyelamatkan anak elf
merupakan tindakan yang mulia.

141
00:10:30,231 --> 00:10:32,731
{You don't seem to be a bad man.} Kelihatannya kau bukanlah orang jahat.

142
00:10:34,391 --> 00:10:36,311
{Are you a mercenary?} Apa kau tentara bayaran?

143
00:10:36,921 --> 00:10:38,411
{Well, something like that.} Yah, begitulah.

144
00:10:38,411 --> 00:10:40,241
{I can't say I approve much} Aku tidak bisa mengatakan aku setuju

145
00:10:40,241 --> 00:10:43,711
{of a business that involves
killing people for money.} dengan bisnis yang melibatkan pembunuhan orang lain untuk mencari uang.

146
00:10:43,711 --> 00:10:46,571
{No, even to help another,} Tidak, bahkan demi membantu orang lain,

147
00:10:46,571 --> 00:10:49,481
{you shouldn't kill a human being so easily.} seharusnya kau tidak membunuh manusia semudah itu.

148
00:10:49,481 --> 00:10:51,861
{This is why I don't like monks.} Inilah kenapa aku tidak suka biarawan.

149
00:10:51,861 --> 00:10:53,371
{Don't be that way.} Jangan begitu.

150
00:10:53,371 --> 00:10:57,681
{My nephew left home, saying he'd
make his name with his sword.} Keponakanku pergi dari rumah, dan mengatakan namanya akan dikenang dengan pedangnya.

151
00:10:57,681 --> 00:11:00,631
{Five years ago, he died on the battlefield,} Lima tahun lalu, dia meninggal di medan perang,

152
00:11:00,631 --> 00:11:02,511
{just a nameless foot soldier.} hanya sebagai tentara tak bernama.

153
00:11:02,511 --> 00:11:04,761
{If he had stayed alive,} Kalau dia masih hidup,

154
00:11:04,761 --> 00:11:08,161
{he would have had a family,
and some happiness with it.} dia pasti akan memiliki keluarga,
dan hidup bahagia.

155
00:11:08,161 --> 00:11:09,611
{How foolish.} Sungguh bodoh.

156
00:11:09,891 --> 00:11:11,521
Bagus malah.

157
00:11:11,861 --> 00:11:15,271
{No matter the cause, he died
doing what he wanted, right?} Mau bagaimanapun keadaannya, dia mati karena melakukan apa yang diinginkannya, 'kan?

158
00:11:15,531 --> 00:11:17,781
{I'd call him a lucky man.} Aku menyebutnya pria yang beruntung.

159
00:11:19,481 --> 00:11:21,821
{Though, once you're dead, that's it.} Meskipun, setelah kau mati,
semua sudah berakhir.

160
00:11:22,641 --> 00:11:24,281
Dari titik itu,
tidak ada lagi jalan untuk maju.

161
00:11:26,761 --> 00:11:29,571
{Sorry, I'll be getting some rest now.} Maaf, aku mau istirahat dulu.

162
00:11:35,121 --> 00:11:36,921
Biar enggak kena demam.

163
00:12:37,921 --> 00:12:39,981
{You won't be able to escape.} Kau tidak akan bisa lari.

164
00:13:01,241 --> 00:13:02,461
Griffith!

165
00:13:14,241 --> 00:13:15,481
{Hey, what's wrong?} Hei, ada apa?

166
00:13:16,201 --> 00:13:18,011
{Whoa, whoa!} Woah, woah!

167
00:13:20,641 --> 00:13:22,461
{What is that?} Apa itu?

168
00:13:22,901 --> 00:13:24,081
Syaitan.

169
00:13:24,321 --> 00:13:27,531
{An evil spirit that makes people see
nightmares, to feed on terror.} Roh jahat yang membuat orang-orang dapat melihat mimpi buruk, dan menghantuinya.

170
00:13:27,531 --> 00:13:28,991
{An evil spirit?} Roh jahat?

171
00:13:28,991 --> 00:13:31,341
{Then what you said earlier...} Kalau begitu yang baru saja kau bilang...

172
00:13:31,341 --> 00:13:34,371
{What, you believe in God,
but not evil spirits?} Apa, kau percaya pada Tuhan, tapi tidak dengan roh jahat?

173
00:13:34,371 --> 00:13:35,811
{Why is something like that here?} Kenapa syaitan ada di sini?

174
00:13:35,811 --> 00:13:37,501
{This attracts them.} Inilah yang memancing mereka.

175
00:13:38,611 --> 00:13:39,651
{A brand?} Tanda?

176
00:13:40,931 --> 00:13:42,251
Ada apa?

177
00:13:48,391 --> 00:13:50,391
Tetaplah di dalam.

178
00:13:50,371 --> 00:13:52,651
Syaitan terlahir dari tubuh orang mati.

179
00:13:52,651 --> 00:13:54,981
Dulu, di sini pasti menjadi medan perang.

180
00:13:55,591 --> 00:13:58,021
Roh-roh jahat merasuki mayat-mayat dan menggunakannya untuk menyerang.

181
00:13:58,501 --> 00:14:02,121
Syaitan yang barusan muncul, bisa jadi kejadian lebih berbahaya akan segera muncul.

182
00:14:05,791 --> 00:14:07,331
Wah, wah!

183
00:14:08,311 --> 00:14:09,661
Bodoh, kembali ke dalam!

184
00:14:10,641 --> 00:14:11,741
Tapi...

185
00:14:26,401 --> 00:14:27,761
Collette!

186
00:14:49,841 --> 00:14:51,331
Seharusnya kau lari!

187
00:14:51,331 --> 00:14:52,711
Pergilah kalau memang kau mau pergi.

188
00:14:52,711 --> 00:14:54,711
Kenapa?

189
00:14:54,071 --> 00:14:56,071
Dasar nekat!

190
00:14:54,911 --> 00:14:57,041
Mereka ada banyak...
Kau bisa terbunuh!

191
00:14:57,471 --> 00:14:58,981
Sudah biasa.

192
00:15:27,291 --> 00:15:31,691
Terlalu besar untuk disebut sebuah pedang.

193
00:15:35,651 --> 00:15:40,581
Terlalu besar, tebal, berat,
dan terlalu keras.

194
00:15:43,911 --> 00:15:45,251
Menurut orang-orang,

195
00:15:46,171 --> 00:15:48,171
benda itu sebetulnya besi raksasa.

196
00:15:49,341 --> 00:15:50,701
Luar biasa...

197
00:15:52,201 --> 00:15:53,741
Ada apa, tuan?

198
00:16:00,921 --> 00:16:02,311
Guts!

199
00:16:01,201 --> 00:16:03,201
Diam!

200
00:16:02,311 --> 00:16:04,311
Aku sedang sibuk.

201
00:16:40,311 --> 00:16:41,521
Guts!

202
00:17:02,371 --> 00:17:04,351
Cih, mentok-mentok cuma 20 orang, ya.

203
00:17:04,351 --> 00:17:05,571
Jangan mengeluh.

204
00:17:05,571 --> 00:17:07,831
Melawa satu orang, jumlah
segini sudah lebih dari cukup.

205
00:17:07,831 --> 00:17:10,021
H-Hei, tunggu dulu...

206
00:17:10,921 --> 00:17:12,831
Ada yang aneh.

207
00:17:12,831 --> 00:17:14,831
Huh?

208
00:17:15,981 --> 00:17:17,551
Apa-apaan itu?

209
00:17:17,861 --> 00:17:19,971
Hei, apa orang itu yang—

210
00:18:17,821 --> 00:18:19,321
Apa-apaan ini?

211
00:18:26,831 --> 00:18:28,831
Guts!

212
00:18:49,591 --> 00:18:53,611
Kau terlalu payah untuk
menjadi kayu bakar!

213
00:19:38,651 --> 00:19:41,561
Itu bukan... salahmu.

214
00:19:45,101 --> 00:19:47,101
Huh?

215
00:19:46,941 --> 00:19:49,591
Ya, betul. Tepat sekali.

216
00:19:50,111 --> 00:19:53,261
Hanya orang lemah yang akan terbunuh
dalam pertarungan orang lain.

217
00:19:54,241 --> 00:19:57,141
Kalau kau tidak bisa hidup bebas
seperti yang kau inginkan,

218
00:19:58,251 --> 00:19:59,781
sebaiknya kau mati saja.

219
00:20:09,671 --> 00:20:11,231
Aku hanya petaka

220
00:20:11,231 --> 00:20:14,571
bagi mereka berdua yang tidak mempunyai kekuatan
untuk melindungi diri mereka sendiri.

221
00:20:14,871 --> 00:20:16,471
Hanya itu yang kutahu.

222
00:20:19,031 --> 00:20:21,771
Aku takkan bisa melangkah sejengkal saja

223
00:20:21,771 --> 00:20:23,781
kalau terus membiarkan diriku
berada dalam masalah.

224
00:20:28,291 --> 00:20:29,811
Tidak berguna.

225
00:20:29,811 --> 00:20:31,541
Kau takkan bisa kabur.

226
00:20:31,541 --> 00:20:33,601
Kemanapun kau pergi...

227
00:20:33,601 --> 00:20:35,691
...kami akan tetap ada.

228
00:20:35,691 --> 00:20:38,301
Kami akan selalu berada di dekatmu.

229
00:20:38,301 --> 00:20:39,851
Kau takkan bisa kabur.

230
00:20:39,851 --> 00:20:42,181
Kami akan selalu mengawasimu.

231
00:20:42,181 --> 00:20:44,201
Kau milikku.

232
00:20:44,201 --> 00:20:46,241
Kau milik kami.

233
00:20:46,241 --> 00:20:49,361
Darah, daging, dan tulangmu...

234
00:20:49,361 --> 00:20:50,511
Telinganya.

235
00:20:50,861 --> 00:20:52,031
Matanya.

236
00:20:52,031 --> 00:20:53,561
Hatinya.

237
00:20:53,561 --> 00:20:55,651
Aku ingin hatinya.

238
00:20:55,731 --> 00:20:57,951
Selama tanda itu tetao ada...

239
00:20:57,951 --> 00:21:01,151
Pastinya, selama kau memiliki tanda itu...

240
00:21:01,151 --> 00:21:03,521
...kau takkan bisa kabur.

241
00:21:03,521 --> 00:21:05,521
Kemanapun kau pergi...

242
00:21:05,521 --> 00:21:07,571
...kau milik kami.

243
00:21:08,261 --> 00:21:10,921
Kemarahan dan kesedihanmu...

244
00:21:10,251 --> 00:21:12,251
Diam.

245
00:21:10,921 --> 00:21:12,241
Rasa sakitmu...

246
00:21:11,831 --> 00:21:12,981
Diam.

247
00:21:12,241 --> 00:21:14,081
Dan rasa takutmu...

248
00:21:14,451 --> 00:21:17,081
Semuanya milik kami.

249
00:21:17,581 --> 00:21:19,341
Diam!

250
00:21:46,361 --> 00:21:47,701
Jadi...

251
00:21:48,871 --> 00:21:50,901
Inilah dunia yang Guts tinggali.

252
00:23:50,251 --> 00:23:52,031
Akhirnya kami menemukanmu,

253
00:23:52,031 --> 00:23:53,531
Pendekar pedang hitam!

254
00:23:56,991 --> 00:24:01,461
Cuplikan Episode Selanjutnya

255
00:24:03,461 --> 00:24:05,461
Inilah Pendekar Pedang Hitam...

256
00:24:07,501 --> 00:24:09,551
Kejahatannya sudah jelas.

257
00:24:11,511 --> 00:24:13,511
<font size="36">Aku Azan, Wakil Komandan Ksatria Rantai Besi Kudus!</font>

258
00:24:15,511 --> 00:24:17,511
Oh, Tonio! Dia orang baik...

259
00:24:19,521 --> 00:24:21,521
